{"tid":697710,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"單親媽媽有米有市場 楊思琦心思思買獨立屋","createTime":"2018-06-11T06:45:57.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-11T08:35:21.000Z","uid":22349,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"1e96e29e08731e9b14ba1f97b55c8a8dc962c64e","tid":697710,"uid":22349,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-11T06:45:57.000Z","msg":"藝人楊思琦日前在馬來西亞為一個樓盤活動擔任剪綵嘉賓，她笑言當地難得陽光普照，避開香港狂風暴雨。問到會否有興趣在馬來西亞置業？思琦坦言﹕「呢邊冇香港咁密集，所以我都想喺度買間獨立屋，得閒就可以帶埋小朋友一齊過嚟度假，都幾好。」她透露稍後要到內地拍戲一個月，希望八月趁暑假加上其生日月可以跟囡囡一齊到馬來西亞旅行。"},{"pid":"fd8ce9184b447a61615885033fdca8cb354adbf3","tid":697710,"uid":22349,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-11T06:46:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20180611/photo/bkn-20180611024557379-0611_00862_001_03p.jpg?20180611095738\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fentertainment%2F20180611%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20180611024557379-0611_00862_001_03p.jpg%3F20180611095738&h=6fb7eff5&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"f758dd0eebf1e0d3e6b9ac7820843bd7b0988e3e","tid":697710,"uid":82917,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-11T06:49:00.000Z","msg":"吳帥<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4015b2722e211da96c176dce49087e63c083a8c9","tid":697710,"uid":58552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-11T07:09:10.000Z","msg":"襯仲有d本錢 出黎做啦"},{"pid":"c9bf8d366f9a06d8196cf2f16eca19f59c2d1302","tid":697710,"uid":41343,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"fd8ce9184b447a61615885033fdca8cb354adbf3","tid":697710,"uid":22349,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-11T06:46:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20180611/photo/bkn-20180611024557379-0611_00862_001_03p.jpg?20180611095738\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https:/